<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>SCVMM 2008 R2 SP1 Server (64 bit)</Title><Description>This detects if the Microsoft System Center Virtual Machine Manager 2008 R2 Server product is installed. 
Also detects that the VMMService is installed (this service is not installed if "/prep"  option is given at setup.  This update should not be offered if the VMMService is not installed, only after the entire setup process is complete).
This is 64 bit only.
</Description></LocalizedProperties>